search_results.title: Cross Canadian Ragweed
search_results.snippet: Cross Canadian Ragweed is an American country and rock band formed in Yukon, Oklahoma in 1994. The original members of the band is how the name was formed.

search_results.title: Cross Canadian Ragweed
search_results.snippet: Country music group Cross Canadian Ragweed consists of Cody Canada, Randy Ragsdale, Grady Cross, and Jeremy Plato. They specialize in the Red Dirt sound.
